ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 49 Medical Officer and Other Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 18, 2025, 15:23 IST
 National Health Mission
 49 Jobs |  Posted On : 18-Aug-2025 |  Odisha |  Salary : 20,000 to 65,000




FOLLOW

The Zilla Swasthya Samiti Kandhamal (ZSS Kandhamal) has officially released a notification for 49 Medical Officers, Physiotherapists, Dental Technicians, Data Assistants/Accountants, and other positions. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, BDS, Post Graduation, BHMS, BAMS, Any Degree, MS/ MD can grab this chance and apply for the ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025. Here we include the age limit, selection process, and salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can attend the interview at the address given below.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Odisha.

ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Medical Officer	06	MBBS
Phsiotherapist	01	MS/ MD
Dental Technician	01	BDS
Data Assistant/ Accountant 	01	Any Degree
Medical Officer Ayush	35	BAMS, BHMS
Visit the official notification for more vacancy details and educational qualifications

Age Limit for the ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 60 years.

Selection Process for the ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 20,000 /- per month
The Maximum Salary: Rs. 65,000 / per month.

Application fee for the ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025

There is no application fee.
How to Apply for the ZSS Kandhamal Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Medical Officer Posts.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Download the application form.
Fill out the application form carefully.
Then, attend the interview at the address mentioned in the official notification.

Important Dates

Date of Walk-in-Interview	03-09-2025
